    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Among Azerbaijani healthcare workers (HCWs), compared to primary vaccine series, CoronaVac booster relative vaccine effectiveness was 60% (95% CI:25\u201379) and 79% (95% CI:44\u201392) against symptomatic and medically attended illness, respectively, during an Omicron BA.1/BA.2 period. Our results support timely CoronaVac booster uptake among Azerbaijani HCWs to reduce morbidity.</jats:p>",
